    "title": "Welcome to Updater",
    "version": "1.0.18",
    "description": "Assembly: updater, Version=1.0.18.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null\nInformation:\nupdater.exe save configuration(updaterConfig.json) of previus call,\nand later can call only with changed arguments\nSamples:\nUpload SomeFreeApp To Update Server:\nupdater.exe -c Upload -u http://localhost:5000 -a SomeFreeApp -e SomeFreeApp.dll\nUpdate SomePrivateApp From Update Server:\nupdater.exe -c Update -u http://localhost:5000 -a SomePrivateApp -e SomePrivateApp.dll -t Qwerty123\nReturns:\n0    Success\n1    Service call fail\n2    Arguments exception"
